<section id="reflection" class="reflection">

<span class="section-tag">
FINAL REFLECTION
</span>

<h2>What I Learned</h2>

<div class="reflection-card">

<h3>❤️ HeartStart Was My Favorite Project</h3>

<p>

HeartStart brought together everything I had learned throughout Introduction to Engineering Design. Instead of simply completing another assignment, I was solving a real problem through research, brainstorming, CAD, prototyping, testing, and redesign.

</p>

<p>

More than anything else, this project taught me that engineering is rarely about getting something right on the first attempt. It's about constantly improving your design until it becomes the best solution possible.

</p>

<div class="reflection-grid">

<div class="reflection-box">

<h4>Biggest Lesson</h4>

<p>

Failure is simply another step in the design process.

</p>

</div>

<div class="reflection-box">

<h4>Favorite Project</h4>

<p>

❤️ HeartStart

</p>

</div>

<div class="reflection-box">

<h4>Most Valuable Skill</h4>

<p>

Learning to redesign instead of giving up.

</p>

</div>

<div class="reflection-box">

<h4>Looking Back</h4>

<p>

IED confirmed that Mechanical Engineering was the right path for me.

</p>

